    'en_US' => '<div><p>As part of the submission process, the authors must check that they comply with all the following conditions. Where these instructions are not respected, submissions may be returned to the authors.</p></div><div><ol><li>The original may not have been published previously nor been previously submitted to any other journal.</li><li>The submission file is in OpenOffice, Microsoft Word, RTF or WordPerfect document format.</li><li>Where possible, the URL for references shall be provided.</li><li>The text complies with the stylistic and bibliographic requirements set out in the author instructions <a href="/ojs/index.php/mayurqua/about/submissions#authorGuidelines" target="_new">Author guidelines</a>, found in the \'About the journal\' section.</li></ol></div>',
